<div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
<aside class="quote no-group" data-username="adt" data-post="3" data-topic="174">
<div class="title">
<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img alt="" width="20" height="20" src="https://mlmmlm.icu/user_avatar/mlmmlm.icu/adt/40/204_2.png" class="avatar"> adt:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>greatly destroyed the bourgeois world outlook and greatly established the proletarian world outlook, as an urgent requirement, it is put in front of economic theory workers (not just economic theory workers).</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>greatly destroying the bourgeois world outlook and greatly establishing the proletarian world outlook, as an urgent requirement, is put in front of economic theory workers (not just economic theory workers).</p>
</div>
